translate Japanese ch1_main_653343b5:

    # "What a wonderful weekend tonight !"
    "激動の1週間が過ぎた。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:10
translate Japanese ch1_main_5d2ac15f:

    # "Now I'm spacing out for a while,sitting on the bed in my room."
    "俺は今、自室のベッドに腰掛けてぼんやりしている。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:11
translate Japanese ch1_main_8349ec7c:

    # "Sayori, my childhood friend, invited me to the literature club. It was the flashpoint."
    "そもそもは、幼馴染のサヨリに連れられて文芸部のドアを開けたこと。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:12
translate Japanese ch1_main_51db8fb8:

    # "I met Queen Monika again."
    "憧れのモニカとの再会、"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:13
translate Japanese ch1_main_eafc5485:

    # "(well,she is sometimes ironical with her beautiful smile on the face)"
    "(あの子、時々最高の笑顔のまま痛いとこ突いてくるんだよな)"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:14
translate Japanese ch1_main_1f66c4bf:

    # "Spent hours with Natsuki, reading her manga together."
    "ナツキといっしょにマンガを読んで過ごした時間、"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:15
translate Japanese ch1_main_c23afb22:

    # "(umm,Parfait Girls. She really really loves it. IDK why)"
    "(といっても『パフェガールズ』だけ。どんだけ好きなんだあのマンガ)"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:16
translate Japanese ch1_main_b51134ef:

    # "Oh, Yuri came to my room."
    "そうだ、ユリがこの部屋に来たんだ。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:17
translate Japanese ch1_main_2ffd2e85:

    # "(I've never invited any girls to my house, as long as I can remenber.)"
    "(記憶する限り、女の子が家に来るなんて初めてだ)"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:18
translate Japanese ch1_main_cb64e404:

    # "And..."
    "そして……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:19
translate Japanese ch1_main_85334a79:

    # "I confessed to Sayori. Yes,I did it."
    "俺はサヨリに告白した。告白してしまった。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:20
translate Japanese ch1_main_8b73fc99:

    # "It's just a couple hours ago."
    "それが数時間前のできごと。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:21
translate Japanese ch1_main_98432c14:

    # "I think I did the right thing, but..."
    "間違ったことをしたとは思わない。ただ……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:22
translate Japanese ch1_main_3a57ada9:

    # "I don't know. I just don't know."
    "わからない。サヨリは……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:23
translate Japanese ch1_main_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:24
translate Japanese ch1_main_d77d0f88:

    # "She said that she liked it to be the way as it used to be."
    "サヨリは「今までどおりでいい」と言った。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:25
translate Japanese ch1_main_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:26
translate Japanese ch1_main_c40a1438:

    # "Ok boy, stop thinking too much. And tomorrow is the festival."
    "考えてもしょうがない。明日は文化祭だ。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:28
translate Japanese ch1_main_4c62b133:

    # "Have a good night. Tomorrow's just another day."
    "とりあえず眠ろう。明日は明日でなんとかなるさ。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:29
translate Japanese ch1_main_c1ff40bf:

    # "Night night."
    "おやすみ。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:30
translate Japanese ch1_main_a20cefa7_2:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:31
translate Japanese ch1_main_50a43eae:

    # "I think I have to do something . What...?"
    "何かを忘れている気がする。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:32
translate Japanese ch1_main_0c51d438:

    # "What...something important to me..."
    "なんだろう？なにか大切なことを……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:35
translate Japanese ch1_main_7e7f0320:

    # "Jeez, I can't remember it."
    "クソッ、思い出せない。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:36
translate Japanese ch1_main_9c676c0f:

    # "Hello darkness, my old friend. It covers me slowly and,"
    "やがて、頭にゆっくりともやがかかり始める"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:37
translate Japanese ch1_main_0d9dfda7:

    # "I fall into sleep."
    "俺は眠りに落ちた。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:45
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_d636b554:

    # "...Hmm?"
    "……なんだこれ。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:46
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_0a417d79:

    # "Am I dreaming?"
    "ああ、夢か。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:47
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_f2d7052c:

    # "Yeah, I'm dreaming now."
    "夢見てんだな、今。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:48
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_6f41555c:

    # "A lucid dream, huh?"
    "{rb}明{/rb}{rt}めい{/rt}{rb}晰{/rb}{rt}せき{/rt}{rb}夢{/rb}{rt}む{/rt}ってやつか。今、俺は夢を見ていて……"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:49
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_ee20c268:

    # "...and what is this?"
    "……で、なんだこれは。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:50
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_ecd4b6f9:

    # "I faintly see the figures of men...in white robes...?"
    "白衣の男たち……？"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:54
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:59
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_01ce0a95:

    # "I don't know why but,"
    "理由はわからない。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:60
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_7c8b5bea:

    # "They scare me."
    "ただ、俺は白衣の男たちが怖い。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch1.rpy:61
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_a8d1fee3:

    # "...and they turned to me."
    "……奴らがこっちを見た。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:62
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_bb6c0f26:

    # "I must escape right now ,or..."
    "逃げなきゃ、ここから。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:63
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_3137164f:

    # "But my body won't move as I intend."
    "なのに体が動かない。"

# game/script-ch1.rpy:64
translate Japanese ch1_1_main_dbaf1398:

    # "Goddamn!!"
    "畜生！！"

translate Japanese strings:
    old "Wake up!"
    new "起きろ！"
